{"tid":761092,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"霸氣嫩媽神招防小孩亂開抽屜 網友全歪樓：這腿我可以玩10","createTime":"2018-07-30T06:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T11:58:11.000Z","uid":82829,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"227bd5905a0f75b66fe43ec4b878f5b189286e3e","tid":761092,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:04:43.000Z","msg":"年輕媽媽超霸氣防止兒子亂開抽屜，網友卻全歪樓在美腿上<br />\n<br />\n不少家長對於好奇心旺盛的小寶寶總是特別苦惱，只要離開視線幾秒，就有可能會闖下大禍。一名年輕媽媽為了防止調皮的小兒子亂來，於是在洗碗的時候也把小兒子帶在身邊，又為了防止他亂開抽屜，直接抬起一條腿，霸氣撐在抽屜口，讓網友全歪樓「這腿我可以」。<br />\n<br />\n這名女網友在臉書「爆廢公社」PO文說：「媽媽日常，帶小孩洗碗，防開抽屜之術」，透過照片可以看到，這名長髮年輕媽媽穿著熱褲在洗碗，並把小孩安置在旁邊的椅子上，接著直接抬起一條腿踩在抽屜口上，防止調皮的小寶貝亂開抽屜，整個霸氣外漏。<br />\n<br />\n網友們紛紛歪樓：「抱歉，我只有看到腿」、「媽媽身材真好」、「這腿我可以玩10年啊！」，還有人揶揄：「小心老公直接從背後偷襲妳」，媽媽看到後也笑回：「沒有爸爸不需要擔心偷襲」，但網友更是繼續歪樓：「沒有老公那是誰拍的！」、「沒關係，我可以應徵現成老爸」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180725000016-260405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180725000016-260405&d=GabojfsCkB0Nh5lPrhQ4ktr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=dbadb1b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180725000016-260405</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GkOT55l.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGkOT55l.png&h=cd7c2068&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7db240ef524d32dd5b47ad27e496e9f6f37a47a","tid":761092,"uid":12008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a93e504054514de5588759dc11b34ae05b4cd9a","tid":761092,"uid":82829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:11:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8520a37aa1d3a165c003d0f9d33ad69736da6a30","tid":761092,"uid":90,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/141547_1d61a9355857ec4a0e87434a71365278.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F141547_1d61a9355857ec4a0e87434a71365278.gif&h=ce8cde9e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"034d5c7511f25f23f879d00cc7c1512a50cea956","tid":761092,"uid":129221,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:47:48.000Z","msg":"影相個個湊b唔好？"},{"pid":"ae596417f28c7c7233e5936cf643719c0b965f3c","tid":761092,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa31163b231bdd670b2c57213675e906b36d0682","tid":761092,"uid":164167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:02:38.000Z","msg":"親子活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係老公就瘋狂奶 <br />\n奶到佢縮腳比個仔開櫃筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f550a5b8f834c331303f6135449ecf9046f030c4","tid":761092,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:26:07.000Z","msg":"我奶腳踝"},{"pid":"40b7fd73c34ca3f796434f28de250a38a0069d97","tid":761092,"uid":88312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:48:56.000Z","msg":"你哋個個都要腳，都無位比我啦，我唯有要兩腿中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7f57a11a404785a7da0b9ec6a461179f4de75a","tid":761092,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa31163b231bdd670b2c57213675